Great to have all three movies in one collection and in the Blue ray format.

Beautiful, sharp hi-def Blu-Ray picture on all 3 movies, was pleasantly surprised in this regard. A great deal at $18.00 and change for all 3 together.

All 3 films are good for lots of laughs, I am not so critical of one or another as are other reviewers.  None are the funniest or most clever films you will ever see, nor the most original, but all 3 are good comedy films with a laugh a minute.
